1. Install Webserver

sudo apt-get install apache2 php5 libapache2-mod-php5 php5-curl

2. Copy files into Webserver

mkdir /var/www/html/wawisionspooler

3. Extract tar

tar xvzf wawision_drucker_spooler.tar.gz -C /var/www/html/wawisionspooler

4. chown -R www-data:www-data /var/www/html/wawisionspooler

5. Configure Spooler over browser http://localhost/wawisionspooler

6. Add to crontab:

crontab -e

php5 /var/www/html/wawisionspooler/cronapi.php
